text: @DWUhlfelderLaw Much was said when #Florida deaths from #pneumonia jumped from around 800 per year to over 5,000 in first 6 months of 2020. Politifact says these numbers don’t indicate unreported #COVID19 deaths. Those deaths occurred prior to testing, so they won’t be included by coroners. ☠️
